Task To-Do List
This is a simple and interactive Task To-Do List application that helps users manage their daily tasks efficiently. The application allows users to add, edit, mark as complete, and delete tasks with an intuitive user interface.

Features
Add Tasks: Easily add new tasks with a title and optional description.
Mark as Complete: Toggle tasks between completed and pending status.
Edit Tasks: Update task details anytime.
Delete Tasks: Remove tasks that are no longer needed.
Responsive Design: Works seamlessly across devices (mobile, tablet, desktop).
Local Storage: Tasks are saved locally, ensuring persistence even after refreshing the browser.

Technologies Used
Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
